Description: KernKlaw-Linux â€” AI assistant daemon for Linux
 A fully native C implementation of the KernKlaw AI assistant,
 designed for Linux (Ubuntu/Fedora/NixOS). Features:
  - Local AI inference via Ollama
  - eBPF-based system monitoring
  - io_uring async I/O
  - Skill plugin system with seccomp sandboxing
  - Lobster-inspired workflow DSL
  - Systemd integration (sd_notify, journald)
